Sentrachem results now due Thursday . Half year results from South African chemicals group Sentrachem Ltd will be released on Thursday , instead of Wednesday as originally expected . " The board meeting is going on a little longer than expected , " a company spokeswoman said . Analysts polled by Reuters forecast Sentrachem ' s earnings for the six months ended February 28 sliding into loss , ranging between 60 . 0 and 80 . 0 cents a share with consensus at 68 . 3 cents versus 55 cents profit in the same period last year . The company was not expected to declare a dividend in the interim period . - - Johannesburg newsroom 27 11 482 1003 
